First abdominal tergite of female with 16–22 short setae in two submedial fields (range 7–12 per field); second to fifth abdominal tergites with short setae with posterior and lateral setae longest; fifth (pregenital) sternite with 54–71 short setae (lateral pair longest) in two submedial fields (range 27–36 per field) (
